name: GetPropertyDetails
description:
Retrieve details of properties for a specific organization.

This tool accesses property details for a specific organization using the Entrata API. It should be called when detailed property information is needed, such as for property management or listings.

parameters.name: client_subdomain
parameters.description: The subdomain representing the specific client or organization for which property details are requested.

parameters.name: property_request_body
parameters.description: The JSON array containing the request details for fetching property information. This should include any necessary filters or criteria.

parameters.name: page_number
parameters.description: The current page number to retrieve in a paginated response.

value_schema.description: The page number of paginated respons.

parameters.name: items_per_page
parameters.description: Number of items to return per page in the response.

value_schema.description: The number of items returned in the respnose

parameters.name: include_pagination_links
parameters.description: Set to 1 to include pagination links in the response; 0 to exclude them.

value_schema.description: Send Pagination Links in Response Body.
